oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Sgt. Horace Collins, veteran of WWI
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A photograph of Horace Collins in civilian clothes, probably taken just after his return home from the war. He is wearing a felt hat and a stiff collared shirt under a coat. Inscribed on the reverse "Horace Earl Collins @ 1920." Sgt. Horace E. Collins served in Co. E, 105th Supply Train, 55th Depot Brigade. Collins was from St. Elmo in Hamilton County, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Collins, Horace E.
